  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Experienced Sales Executive – Commercial Vehicle Workshop",
  "description": "<h3>Job Description:</h3><p>We are looking for an experienced and driven Sales Executive with a strong background in commercial vehicle workshops to join our team. The ideal candidate will be responsible for promoting workshop services, expanding our customer base, and building long-term relationships with fleet owners and corporate clients.</p><h3>Key Responsibilities:</h3><ul><li><p>Bring in new workshop sales and service jobs for commercial vehicles</p></li><li><p>Manage existing customer accounts and maintain strong relationships</p></li><li><p>Prepare quotations, follow up on approvals, and close sales</p></li><li><p>Follow up on outstanding payments and ensure timely collection</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with accounts and operations teams on billing and payment status</p></li><li><p>Liaise with customers on invoicing, credit terms, and payment schedules</p></li><li><p>Ensure accurate documentation and job completion before invoicing</p></li></ul><h3>Requirements:</h3><ul><li><p>Minimum <strong>2–3 years of sales experience</strong> in <strong>commercial vehicle / truck / fleet workshop</strong></p></li><li><p>Strong understanding of commercial vehicle servicing and maintenance</p></li><li><p>Good communication, negotiation, and interpersonal skills</p></li><li><p>Self-motivated, target-driven, and independent</p></li><li><p>Possess own vehicle (preferred)</p></li><li><p>Existing industry contacts will be an advantage<br /></p></li></ul><h3>Benefits:</h3><ul><li><p>Competitive basic salary + attractive commission</p></li><li><p>Supportive and professional working environment<br /></p><p><strong>SINGAPOREAN / PR ONLY</strong></p></li></ul>",
